<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to OCMS!</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset and basic styling */
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    /* Email wrapper styling */
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    /* Header styling */
    .email-header {
      background-color: #000000;
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    /* Body styling */
    .email-body {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .email-body p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .activation-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    /* Footer styling */
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .email-footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    /* Button styling */
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to OCMS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with OCMS. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
      <h2 class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></h2>
      <p>The activation code expires in 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you did not register for an OCMS account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:acnilesupport@gmail.com">acnilesupport@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
